lished date'=>'發佈日期','Sticky posts'=>'置頂文章','Ping status'=>'內容更新通知狀態','Comment status'=>'留言狀態','Custom fields'=>'自訂欄位','Taxonomies'=>'分類法','Settings saved.'=>'設定已儲存。','Translations updated.'=>'譯文已更新。','Strings translations'=>'字串譯文','About Polylang'=>'關於 Polylang','The language was created, but the WordPress language file was not downloaded. Please install it manually.'=>'語言已建立，但是尚未下載 WordPress 語言套件檔案，請手動安裝對應的語言套件。','Filters content by language'=>'依據語言篩選內容','Show all languages'=>'顯示全部語言','Settings'=>'設定','Widget text'=>'小工具文字','Widget title'=>'小工具標題','Language switcher'=>'語言切換器','The language must have a name'=>'這個語言必須有語言名稱。','The language code must be unique'=>'語言代碼必須是唯一的項目。','The language code contains invalid characters'=>'語言代碼包含無效字元。','Enter a valid WordPress locale'=>'輸入有效的 WordPress 地區語言','Language updated.'=>'語言已更新。','Language deleted.'=>'語言已刪除。','Language added.'=>'語言已新增。','Impossible to add the language.'=>'無法新增這個語言。','All languages'=>'全部語言','The widget is displayed for:'=>'這個小工具的顯示位置:','None'=>'無','Sets the language'=>'設定語言','Edit'=>'編輯','(no parent)'=>'(無上層項目)','Languages'=>'語言','Language'=>'語言','&mdash; No Change &mdash;'=>'&mdash; 不變更 &mdash;']];